{"tid":302717,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 真三國無雙斬(66) 公平咩","createTime":"2017-06-29T14:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T14:59:13.000Z","uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c393b34a928a264a4f268b34db57139119984ace","tid":302717,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Y61dd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Y61dd8.jpg&h=698f98ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIOS : <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1131126249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1131126249&d=Jkk4H3fGldFjjD1F5YmC2Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=bd58a6da\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1131126249</a><br />\n<br />\nAN : <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nexon.dynastywarriors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nexon.dynastywarriors&d=Jkk4H3fGldFjjD1F5YmC2Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=ac52ac4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nexon.dynastywarriors</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A 睇左先好問</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1)  洗唔洗刷首抽 ?</span></span></strong><br />\n刷首抽game 唔刷就開局又唔課金會好辛苦   <br />\n<br />\n問: 如何刷首抽 : <br />\n答: AN機同IOS機都1樣 , 沒分別<br />\n先預備大量GMAIL (點樣大量申請自己諗啦 , 有電話認證限制)<br />\n做完教學記得去收信 , 會多幾抽<br />\n然後去 右上去設定 -&gt; 資訊 -&gt;綁定GMAIL-&gt;然後登出-&gt;再用遊客登入<br />\n(佢有個制係刪除帳號有冇用 ? 答你係無用既 , 一定要綁定登出先刷到) BY NEAR<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2)  點先可以開局 ?</span></span></strong><br />\n首先要知咩係啱屬 : 卡片背後會有顏色 , 金底即代表岩屬 , 能力值亦會係該角色中最高<br />\n自行參考下圖 , 紅框代表錯屬 , 黃框內代表岩屬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3crd56B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3crd56B.jpg&h=a105ac42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳國 火屬<br />\n魏國 水屬<br />\n蜀國 木屬<br />\n他國 火屬<br />\n另外亦有武將 唔啱屬都會勁過其他武將啱屬 如各名將 王元姬 呂玲綺<br />\n可參考 (更新版)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/184732_b3610f3708b7a65bb60b7a3241f76bfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F184732_b3610f3708b7a65bb60b7a3241f76bfa.jpg&h=a314d974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(僅作數值比較 參考下好 技能 攻速等亦需考慮)<br />\n<br />\n不過除非你有極限耐性 , 否則唔好追5星6星好局<br />\n只要4星2-3隻啱屬性就可以開局 , 因為到最後都可以升上6星<br />\n只係前期會辛苦小小 當然搵D有得刷技就最好<br />\n包括 周泰 太史慈 董卓等<br />\n關卡掉落可參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=Jkk4H3fGldFjjD1F5YmC2Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=34e326f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3)  佢地話幫角色升技 , 係點升技</span></span></strong><br />\n答: 只要食番自己相同既角色就可以升技 , 例如呂布食呂布 (不過建議金底先好食其他) 升既技能點 = 肥料星數<br />\n金食金 金食銀 都可以 , 部份角色可以刷主線掉落<br />\n最好將肥料升到3星先食 比較慳錢 亦會+3技能等級 <br />\n<br />\n另外 用相同武將升星的話 會有額外技能點 <br />\n4星升5星 = 4+2 , 5星升6星 = 5+3 <br />\n升星時會以下一星級技能上限計數 即使滿左技都可以食左先<br />\n(5星武將技能上限10lv , 6星武將技能上限12lv)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4)  點樣由4星上5星 , 5星上6星</span></span></strong><br />\n答: 只要將要升星既角色升到滿等 , 食其他同星種角色(不需要1樣) , 被食角色不需滿等<br />\n4星上5星要4隻4星肥料 , 5星上6星要 5隻5星肥料<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5)  打到第幾關先會儲到3000元寶10抽 ?</span></span></strong><br />\n玩到你卡關都唔會有 一係等拎登入獎勵 一係課金 <br />\n(十連嘅話我係打到4-3 登入第4日會送元寶 咁就應該夠)BY 潛水會員<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6)  卡關點算   </span></span></strong><br />\n1. 搵好友手動打 試多幾次<br />\n2. 刷關升可以幫角色升星 , 升技 , 刷武器合成等等 , 打番前面既關卡 , 最好刷番你有既角色去升技<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">刷角及其他關卡資料，可以睇呢兩個(呢兩條LINK我未搵到邊個整，知道既話返我知THX)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1toDEosctYL06KypWso9PGYBlS2XX0jQSWw1nIA_g1JA/htmlview#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1toDEosctYL06KypWso9PGYBlS2XX0jQSWw1nIA_g1JA%2Fhtmlview%23&d=Jkk4H3fGldFjjD1F5YmC2Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=60845fe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1toDEosctYL06KypWso9PGYBlS2XX0jQSWw1nIA_g1JA/htmlview#</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">以上資料由巴打Near及及時行落巴打提供</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位巴打唔好再認錯孫權係呂布呀 ! 2隻好似樣</span>(BY Near)</strong>"}]}